      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h2 id=\"Attachingamaterial-AttachingaMaterial\"><style>[data-colorid=lw5cd1u6pi]{color:#192e59} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=lw5cd1u6pi]{color:#a6bbe6}[data-colorid=jqdj6ncyp3]{color:#192e59} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=jqdj6ncyp3]{color:#a6bbe6}</style>Attaching a Material</h2><p>You can attach materials (bxdf's) to selected objects using the shortcuts in the Object Context Menu:</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638358\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c33b9fc1-fdaf-4316-814b-aa0b6246fe7b\" data-media-type=\"file\" /></span><br />This will attach the selected material to the selected objects in the outliner.<br /><br />You can also attach material to an object in the usual way within the Material Properties tab&nbsp;<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"22\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638361\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"material_properties.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"433339f0-2be9-4627-9d4f-a2a02d00647b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22 1x\" /></span>. <br /><br />Click New:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_new.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=445&amp;height=214\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_new.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"214\" data-width=\"445\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638364\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_new.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f208a991-e061-40d7-a266-6b061b56c258\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_new.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=445&amp;height=214 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_new.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=445&amp;height=214 1x\" /></span><p /><p>Then click <strong>Add RenderMan Nodetree&nbsp;</strong></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTree.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=447&amp;height=424\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTree.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"424\" data-width=\"447\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638367\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTree.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d73bb950-5e9b-4e84-8765-dbde4349ae00\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTree.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=447&amp;height=424 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTree.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=447&amp;height=424 1x\" /></span><p /><p>and select the RenderMan material you want to use.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"676\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTreeSelect.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=646&amp;height=609\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTreeSelect.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"609\" data-width=\"646\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638370\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTreeSelect.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e0155ff2-9898-4600-8cf2-1ed72348289f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTreeSelect.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=646&amp;height=609 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTreeSelect.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=646&amp;height=609 1x\" /></span><p /><p>RenderMan shading networks will always terminate with a <span data-colorid=\"lw5cd1u6pi\">RenderMan Material Output </span>node.</p><p>Here's an example shading network:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Network.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=284\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Network.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"504\" data-width=\"1206\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638373\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Network.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"8d1e6cf1-e07e-4375-891d-1105649a15ce\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Network.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1206&amp;height=504 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Network.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=284 1x\" /></span><h2 id=\"Attachingamaterial-Patterns\">Patterns</h2><p>Pattern nodes can be connected to materials or other patterns in the usual way using Shader Editor <span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"19\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/shader_editor.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=27&amp;height=19\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/shader_editor.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638376\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"shader_editor.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"95a130f7-a07e-4349-8d85-e4b328231822\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/shader_editor.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=27&amp;height=19 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/shader_editor.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=27&amp;height=19 1x\" /></span>. or directly within the Material properties Tab&nbsp;<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"22\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638361\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"material_properties.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"433339f0-2be9-4627-9d4f-a2a02d00647b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22 1x\" /></span>. <br />For parameters that can take a pattern connection, a&nbsp;<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"25\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/pattern_connection.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=22&amp;height=25\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/pattern_connection.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638379\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pattern_connection.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1d68b427-a56d-4924-ad1a-5c9802a9c2a2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/pattern_connection.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=22&amp;height=25 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/pattern_connection.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=22&amp;height=25 1x\" /></span>&nbsp;will be shown next to the parameter value. This is our connection widget.&nbsp;</p><p>Clicking on the widget will show our connection menu. Here's an example:</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"676\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Connection_pattern.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=444&amp;height=594\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Connection_pattern.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"594\" data-width=\"444\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638382\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Connection_pattern.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1b4d616a-1315-4633-91f7-61960cd73a42\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Connection_pattern.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=444&amp;height=594 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Connection_pattern.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=444&amp;height=594 1x\" /></span><p>Patterns will be broken up into categories for easier browsing. The __EXISTING__ section will show existing nodes in the shader graph that you can connect to. If the parameter is already connected some more options will appear.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"456\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/pattern_connection3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703242&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=188&amp;height=294\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/pattern_connection3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703242&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"294\" data-width=\"188\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638385\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pattern_connection3.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5f43913d-c5cb-4415-bc17-b3f4cbc6d702\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/pattern_connection3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703242&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=188&amp;height=294 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/pattern_connection3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703242&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=188&amp;height=294 1x\" /></span><p /><p>The top line will show what node is currently connected to this parameter. The Disconnect item will disconnect the parameter from the incoming node. The Remove item will disconnect and remove the incoming node from the graph. Solo Input Node allows you to solo the incoming node. This is useful if you want to concentrate on tweaking the node, independent of the whole material.</p><h2 id=\"Attachingamaterial-AttachingaMaterial.1\">Attaching a Material</h2><p>You can attach materials (bxdf's) to selected objects using the shortcuts in the Object Context Menu:</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638358\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c33b9fc1-fdaf-4316-814b-aa0b6246fe7b\" data-media-type=\"file\" /></span><br />This will attach the selected material to the selected objects in the outliner.<br /><br />You can also attach material to an object in the usual way within the Material Properties tab&nbsp;<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"22\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638361\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"material_properties.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"433339f0-2be9-4627-9d4f-a2a02d00647b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22 1x\" /></span>. <br /><br />Click New:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"629\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_new.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=445&amp;height=214\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_new.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"214\" data-width=\"445\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638364\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_new.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f208a991-e061-40d7-a266-6b061b56c258\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_new.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=445&amp;height=214 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_new.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=445&amp;height=214 1x\" /></span><p /><p>Then click <strong>Add RenderMan Nodetree&nbsp;</strong></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"626\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTree.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=447&amp;height=424\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTree.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"424\" data-width=\"447\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638367\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTree.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d73bb950-5e9b-4e84-8765-dbde4349ae00\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTree.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=447&amp;height=424 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTree.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=447&amp;height=424 1x\" /></span><p /><p>and select the RenderMan material you want to use.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"625\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTreeSelect.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=625&amp;height=589\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTreeSelect.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"609\" data-width=\"646\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638370\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTreeSelect.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e0155ff2-9898-4600-8cf2-1ed72348289f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTreeSelect.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=646&amp;height=609 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_NodeTreeSelect.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=625&amp;height=589 1x\" /></span><p /><p>RenderMan shading networks will always terminate with a <span data-colorid=\"jqdj6ncyp3\">RenderMan Material Output </span>node.</p><p>Here's an example shading network:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"625\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Network.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=625&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Network.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"504\" data-width=\"1206\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638373\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Network.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"8d1e6cf1-e07e-4375-891d-1105649a15ce\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Network.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1206&amp;height=504 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Network.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702856&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=625&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span><h2 id=\"Attachingamaterial-Patterns.1\">Patterns</h2><p>Pattern nodes can be connected to materials or other patterns in the usual way using Shader Editor <span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"19\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/shader_editor.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=27&amp;height=19\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/shader_editor.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638376\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"shader_editor.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"95a130f7-a07e-4349-8d85-e4b328231822\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/shader_editor.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=27&amp;height=19 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/shader_editor.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=27&amp;height=19 1x\" /></span>. or directly within the Material properties Tab&nbsp;<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"22\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638361\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"material_properties.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"433339f0-2be9-4627-9d4f-a2a02d00647b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432702636&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22 1x\" /></span>. <br />For parameters that can take a pattern connection, a&nbsp;<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"25\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/pattern_connection.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=22&amp;height=25\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/pattern_connection.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638379\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pattern_connection.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1d68b427-a56d-4924-ad1a-5c9802a9c2a2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/pattern_connection.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=22&amp;height=25 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/pattern_connection.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=22&amp;height=25 1x\" /></span>&nbsp;will be shown next to the parameter value. This is our connection widget.&nbsp;</p><p>Clicking on the widget will show our connection menu. Here's an example:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"629\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Connection_pattern.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=444&amp;height=594\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Connection_pattern.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"594\" data-width=\"444\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638382\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Connection_pattern.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1b4d616a-1315-4633-91f7-61960cd73a42\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Connection_pattern.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=444&amp;height=594 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/RenderMan_Blender_SelectMaterial_Connection_pattern.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=444&amp;height=594 1x\" /></span><p>Patterns will be broken up into categories for easier browsing. The __EXISTING__ section will show existing nodes in the shader graph that you can connect to. If the parameter is already connected some more options will appear.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"456\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/pattern_connection3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703242&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=188&amp;height=294\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638346/pattern_connection3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703242&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"294\" data-width=\"188\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638385\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pattern_connection3.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5f43913d-c5cb-4415-bc17-b3f4cbc6d702\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/pattern_connection3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703242&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=188&amp;height=294 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638346/pattern_connection3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703242&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=188&amp;height=294 1x\" /></span><p /><p>The top line will show what node is currently connected to this parameter. The Disconnect item will disconnect the parameter from the incoming node. The Remove item will disconnect and remove the incoming node from the graph. Solo Input Node allows you to solo the incoming node. This is useful if you want to concentrate on tweaking the node, independent of the whole material.</p>"
    }
